\cb3 Per-Word Definition: "Values serve as standards of behaviour for determining correct courses of action and influencing personal motivation"\cb1 \
\cb3 Based on the sources, this foundational statement can be defined word-for-word as follows:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'95 
