\cb3 \'95 
\f2\b Standards
\f1\b0 : The "criteria" or "abstract concepts" used to distinguish what a group regards as right, good, or beautiful.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'95 
\f2\b Behaviour
\f1\b0 : The "modes of conduct" or "categories of action" that people adopt in social and professional settings.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'95 
\f2\b Determining
\f1\b0 : The process of "choosing" or "evaluating" between available options based on a judgment of importance.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'95 
